quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,171,"Wa-ith nataqna aljabalafawqahum kaannahu thullatun wathannooannahu waqiAAun bihim khuthoo ma ataynakumbiquwwatin wathkuroo ma feehi laAAallakumtattaqoon"
  7,172,"Wa-ith akhatha rabbuka minbanee adama min thuhoorihim thurriyyatahumwaashhadahum AAala anfusihim alastu birabbikum qaloobala shahidna an taqooloo yawma alqiyamatiinna kunna AAan hatha ghafileen"
  7,173,"Aw taqooloo innama ashraka abaonamin qablu wakunna thurriyyatan min baAAdihimafatuhlikuna bima faAAala almubtiloon"
  7,174,"Wakathalika nufassilu al-ayatiwalaAAallahum yarjiAAoon"
  7,175,"Watlu AAalayhim nabaa allatheeataynahu ayatina fansalakhaminha faatbaAAahu ashshaytanu fakanamina alghaween"
  7,176,"Walaw shi/na larafaAAnahu bihawalakinnahu akhlada ila al-ardi wattabaAAahawahu famathaluhu kamathali alkalbi in tahmilAAalayhi yalhath aw tatruk-hu yalhath thalika mathalualqawmi allatheena kaththaboo bi-ayatinafaqsusi alqasasa laAAallahumyatafakkaroon"
  7,177,"Saa mathalan alqawmu allatheenakaththaboo bi-ayatina waanfusahum kanooyathlimoon"
  7,178,"Man yahdi Allahu fahuwa almuhtadeewaman yudlil faola-ika humu alkhasiroon"
